content: I used this app for 2 years. The app features like pregnancy tracker, kick counter, food&nutrition guide, and child progress tracker have been very useful for me. On the other hand, I find the Q&A community lively, however, it lacks moderation. There are lots of advices containing medical, non-medical, herbal, and home remedies from non-practitioners of medicine and other unqualified individuals. We can't just rely on users to report everything every time. There are also morbid articles.

content: Bagaimana cara ubah usia kehamilan agar sesuai cek usg dengan dokter
replyContent:
Hi Mums, 
Untuk rubah atau reset ulang usia kehamilan dapat dilakukan dengan cara mengubah tanggal "HPHT" atau tanggal "Due Date" sebagai berikut: 1. Klik menu pada pojok kiri atas 2. klik tombol "tambah anak" 3. isi HPHT dan informasi lainnya-> klik simpan 4. Lalu masuk ke profile lagi untuk menghapus data "anak pertama" (data yang salah tsb)
